    G\ar [r, "\eta  G"]\ar [dr, "1_G"'] & GFG\ar [d, "G\epsilon "] \\
     & G\makebox [0pt][l]{.}
  \end {tikzcd}

By the definitions of vertical and whiskered
  composition, it suffices to work in components. To show the left triangle
  identity, it suffices to show that 




