  \begin {tikzcd}
    C\ar [rr, bend left, "F"] & \bot  & D\ar [ll, bend left, "G"]\makebox [0pt][l]\,
  \end {tikzcd}



 be an adjunction. Then the natural
transformation 1_C\xrightarrow {\eta } GF whose component c\xrightarrow {\eta _c} GFc is the transpose of the identity 1_{Fc} is called the unit of the
adjunction.

